                        <interp inst="t18370227-name-1037" type="given" value="EDWARD"></interp>EDWARD KENNEDY</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable K</hi> 218.) In consequence of in<lb></lb>formation from Smith, I went to a house in Twine-court, about a quarter to one o'clock, and found the prisoner—I did not find the sovereign.</p>
